ia","guid":"Vs8j9_8Skz9TOnPWEF7eXg","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"ATIN, atheroembolic disease,\\Nvasculitis, and DRESS syndrome","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"74","text":"fever, morbilliform rash,\\Nand eosinophilia","guid":"atx402CTS6UInNUXX_y1IQ","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"present in < 10%","guid":"akYbOpwfDin6EU5fe9hwGA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"3","text":"Diagnostics","guid":"2f62KUnA0hTgPrOV7GIaag","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"ATIN typically manifests as slowly\\Nprogressive, nonoliguric, intrinsic AKI","guid":"8qTiIg4o7XsX2To9NfB7uQ","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"\\\\*Approach\\\\*","guid":"oh4qPaShuKG2PsoMAiSi_A","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"Determine if the patient fulfills\\Ndiagnostic criteria for AKI","guid":"yCQM6_UN_EAUrD3A4oLCDg","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"Obtain a minimum diagnostic\\Nworkup for patients with\\Nsuspected kidney diseases.","guid":"eMA0O_Q56m-ITWPIF9ao0A","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"Blood tests and\\Nurine studies","guid":"DnBldO4Lq8xlJRNUWzxY-A","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"Renal imaging studies","guid":"BKRE2jsNOrPVmCgziZP7Gw","children":[]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"81","text":"Identify","guid":"_MmLfNh4kdAY84ooA4vUJw","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"characteristic clinical features","guid":"pAYY0y-KgZeD4D8NaJ5ptQ","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"risk factors","guid":"UQry-2lfIg-cudwMHS5loA","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"86","text":"potential exposures for ATIN","guid":"GIngcO2NUd3ZKrv33imXUQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"81","text":"Consider renal biopsy\\Ngold standard test","guid":"EVLgL5Of6F6s8jgwgSgsLQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"79","text":"\\\\*Blood tests\\\\*","guid":"mcisUm-mvIHiM4lt5SXigQ","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"Perfil bioquímico","guid":"40ac-VlJoUG7gkNXlO3gJw","children":[{"id